window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Enrolling at BCU was supposed to be my chance at freedom.</b></p> <p>An escape from my parents who insist I follow in their footsteps as a Guardian of the Society. Keep the members safe—that's what I'm supposed to do. But how can I safeguard the students when I can't even protect myself?</p> <p>Someone has been watching me. His eyes burn into my soul like a branding iron. At night, he haunts my dreams and transforms them into nightmares. Sometimes when I wake, he's there, standing at the foot of my bed in awe of my existence.</p> <p>He isn't the one I fear most, though. Others have their eyes on me, too. Only their obsession runs deeper than Ridge's, and I fear if I fall under their thumbs, I won't make it out of here alive.</p> <p><i>There once was a sicko who lurked in the mist.</i></p> <p><i>He preyed on my soul baring a closed iron fist.</i></p> <p><i>His stare made me itch while his eyes locked me under his spell.</i></p> <p><i>But taking his hand may be my only escape from this hell.</i></p> <p><i>We Will Reign</i> is a dark college romance with mature content. Wicked Boys of BCU is a why-choose romance with a growing harem throughout the series.</p>"; 
